<article class="post--single post-9969 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-uncategorized tag-big-thoughts tag-book tag-family tag-feeding-a-kid tag-memoir tag-teaching tag-travel tag-writing" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/BlogPosting">
  <header class="post-header">
